Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的课都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是在胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没能完成就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚 那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这干这些又能怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算考了个高分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能带我上天国不成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 谁来回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这么巧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就别发牢骚 痛快的干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了达成那个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说说 需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人需要有对抗过去的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人需要有实现梦想的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人需要长久的时间和伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是对抗你的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 什么嘛 这不是能做得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以接下来就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再觉得不公平或迷惑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来学生会室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在那 一直等着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太史无前例了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是叫音无同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会有女朋友的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻说他等着谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神集中的考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 快点坐下
